sempurna, tapi..

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.040
Benar sekali, Ani.

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:18.920
Kami berdua sempurna
satu sama lain.

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:23.560
Jadi, mari kita mulai dari awal

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:26.640
